<driver id="driver/ppmtomd">
 <name>ppmtomd</name>
 <url>http://www.dcs.ed.ac.uk/home/jcb/ppmtomd/</url>
 <execution>
  <filter />
  <prototype>gs -q -dNOPAUSE -dBATCH -dPARANOIDSAFER -sDEVICE=ppmraw -sOutputFile=-%A%B -informat Colour%C</prototype>
 </execution>
 <comments>
  <en>
    This driver works on the MicroDry thermal transfer printers: The
    Alps MD series, the Citizen printiva series, and the Okidata DP
    series. It is the successor of the &quot;ppmtocpva&quot;
    driver.
  </en>
 </comments>
